data.actual_result: It shows an embed of the discordapp wikipedia page
data.expected_result: It shouldn't show an embed since the wikipedia page doesn't exist
data.short_description: Wikipedia embeds ignores everything that's posted before the last slash in the URL
data.steps_to_repro: - Write a message that is: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Discord_(software)- then post a second message with any content you want before discord software, here's an example: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ILoveBugHunters/Discord_(software)
